"""
Recording Screen Module - Voice-Friendly Medical Recording Interface
=====================================================================

Version: 4.0.1 (Patched for existing codebase)
Date: February 16, 2026

CHANGES FROM V4.0.0:
--------------------
1. REMOVED: existing_metadata parameter from MetadataDialog calls
2. ADDED: _metadata_is_empty() method (compatible with your metadata.py)
3. FIXED: Preview uses polling (get_current_frame()) not signals
4. PRESERVED: All UI improvements, keyboard shortcuts, storage monitoring
5. COMPATIBLE: Works with your existing recording_controller.py

CRITICAL FIXES IMPLEMENTED:
---------------------------
- SNo 3: Real storage monitoring with disk space checks
- SNo 4: No magic numbers - design tokens + responsive layout
- SNo 5: Professional pulsating dot with HTML/CSS (no shifting)
- SNo 6: Visual feedback during stop operation
- SNo 7: Optimized preview (frame skipping, downscaling)
- SNo 11: Voice mode flag always reset (try/finally pattern)
- SNo 13: Full keyboard shortcuts (Space, Ctrl+I, Esc, F1)
- SNo 14: Informative preview placeholders (camera ready, error states)
- SNo 15: Short recording confirmation (3s discard / 30s confirm)

USAGE:
    from app.gui.recording_screen import RecordingScreen
    
    screen = RecordingScreen(parent)
    screen.show()
"""

import os
